            // placeholders and the other with inference variables and then
            // equating the instantiated types.
            //
            // We want `for<..> A == for<..> B` -- therefore we want
            // `exists<..> A == for<..> B` and `exists<..> B == for<..> A`.
            // Check if `exists<..> A == for<..> B`
